%% Data plane autoscale and registration
flowchart TB
  Metrics[Node Metrics / Load] -->|High load| Autoscaler[Autoscaler / Orchestrator]
  Autoscaler --> Provisioner[Provisioner (Terraform/Cloud API)]
  Provisioner --> Cloud[Cloud Provider API]
  Cloud --> NewInstance[New VM Instance]
  NewInstance --> Bootstrap[cloud-init / user-data]
  Bootstrap --> Node[VPN Node]
  Node -->|Register| Control[Control Plane API]
  Control -->|Update registry| DB[(Postgres)]
  Node -->|Send metrics| MetricsDB[(Prometheus / TSDB)]
  MetricsDB --> Autoscaler
  Autoscaler -->|Scale down| Provisioner
  NoteRight[Cost & egress monitor triggers scale policy] --> Autoscaler
